• The user will login to the system and his image will be captured along with his GPS location.
All the information will be sent to the admin where admin will view image and GPS location.
• Once logged in, the GPS location of the employee will be tracked automatically by the system and sent to the admin after every 5 minutes.
For tracking GPS location, you may opt for using available GPS libraries in your implementation.
• When user logout the system again the image will be captured as well as GPS location will be sent to the admin.
